trans-unit.source: Specifies the standard keys on a console.

The ConsoleKey enumeration is typically used in the nfo structure, which is returned by the <xref:System.Console.ReadKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to indicate which key on the console has been pressed.
trans-unit.target: Wyliczenie ConsoleKey jest zwykle używana w strukturze nfo, który jest zwracany przez <xref:System.Console.ReadKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metody, aby wskazać, które na konsoli wciśnięciu klawisza.</xref:System.Console.ReadKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
